text: Tereza Vanžurová (born 12 November 1992) is a Czech volleyball player. She played at the 2010 FIVB Volleyball Women's World Championship and 2015 FIVB World Grand Prix. She played for VK Královo Pole Brno. == References == Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Czech volleyball players
